query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, rtrim(PerAd.PlaneAddress) OR1 from PersonCards PerC join PersonAddresses PerAd on PerC.TempAddressId = PerAd.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.TempAddressIsInactive != 1 and PerAd.FiasRegionId is not null and len(PerAd.PlaneAddress) > 0 and PerAd.PlaneAddress not like '  '

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, rtrim(PerAd.PlaneAddress) OR1 from PersonCards PerC join PersonAddresses PerAd on PerC.TempAddressId = PerAd.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.TempAddressIsInactive != 1 and PerAd.FiasRegionId is null and len(PerAd.PlaneAddress) > 0 and PerAd.PlaneAddress not like '  '
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '' OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.TempAddressId is null
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '' OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.TempAddressId is not null and PerC.TempAddressIsInactive = 1
